Class Main.MainWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Main.MainWindow
  • Enclosing class:
    Main

    public static class Main.MainWindow
extends java.lang.Object
    Singleton class to create and show the main window for the app. This window is then used by other parts of the app to add and update relevant GUI components.
    Author:
    michael, kendall
